## 🔐 Phase 2 — Authentication & Authorization

| Check | Status | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| JWT implementation | ⚠️ Partial | JWT exists for rejoin only, not for REST API auth |
| Token expiration | ✅ Good | 24h expiry configured |
| Token storage | ✅ Good | `sessionStorage` (not localStorage) — cleared on tab close |
| CSRF protection | ❌ None | No CSRF tokens on any endpoint |
| RBAC | ⚠️ Basic | Host-only checks for `start_game`, role checks for night actions |
| IDOR | ⚠️ Risk | Vote/kill targets use socketId — attacker could target arbitrary IDs |
| Admin routes | ✅ N/A | No admin routes exist |

