## 🔥 Phase 14 — Zero Trust Review

| Principle | Status | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| **Verify explicitly** | ❌ | WebSocket connections unauthenticated |
| **Least privilege** | ⚠️ | All players receive full player list with socket IDs |
| **Assume breach** | ❌ | No intrusion detection, no security event logging |
| **Defense in depth** | ❌ | Single layer of validation (no WAF, no middleware chain) |

