## 💎 Real-Time Game Session Audit

| Vector | Risk | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| WebSocket hijacking | 🔴 High | No `io.use()` auth middleware |
| Room code brute forcing | 🔴 High | No rate limit on `GET /api/room/:code` + weak PRNG |
| Enumeration attacks | 🟡 Medium | `GET /api/stats` reveals `activeRooms` count → attacker knows search space |
| State desynchronization | 🟡 Medium | No mutex on phase transitions — concurrent events can skip phases |
| Replay token attacks | 🟡 Medium | JWT valid for 24h — stolen token works until expiry |
| Bot flooding rooms | 🔴 High | No CAPTCHA, no WS auth, basic IP rate limit only on `join_room` |

---

## ✅ Secure Deployment Checklist

- [ ] Install and configure `helmet` with strict CSP
- [ ] Install `express-rate-limit` — configure per-route limits
- [ ] Replace `Math.random()` with `crypto.randomBytes()` for room codes
- [ ] HTML-escape all chat messages server-side before broadcast
- [ ] Set `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })`
- [ ] Remove JWT hardcoded fallback secret
- [ ] Remove legacy name-based rejoin (JWT only)
- [ ] Add Socket.IO `io.use()` authentication middleware
- [ ] Add per-event rate limiting for all socket events
- [ ] Use opaque player IDs instead of socket IDs in public payloads
- [ ] Remove unused `qrcode` and `uuid` from backend [package.json](file:///e:/project/MAFIA/backend/package.json)
- [ ] Set `NODE_ENV=production` and `debug: false` in production config
- [ ] Set `LOG_LEVEL=info` or [warn](file:///e:/project/MAFIA/backend/utils/logger.js#31-36) in production
- [ ] Add `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` graceful shutdown handler
- [ ] Add `joinAttempts` Map cleanup interval
- [ ] Set `HSTS`, `X-Frame-Options`, `CSP` headers
- [ ] Enable HTTPS-only (Railway handles this via proxy)
- [ ] Add [.gitignore](file:///e:/project/MAFIA/.gitignore) to `frontend/` directory
- [ ] Audit git history for any committed secrets: `git log --all -p -- '*.env'`
- [ ] Upgrade `express` to 4.21+, `socket.io` to 4.8+
